Titolo: Hyper Scape

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Hyper Scape is a free-to-play first-person shooter battle royale game developed by Ubisoft Montreal and published by Ubisoft for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One. The game is notable for its integration with video game live streamers which allows viewers on  Twitch to affect the outcome of a match.  
The open beta for Microsoft Windows was released on July 12, 2020. The game was released on Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One on August 11, 2020. The game is available on the PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X/S platforms via backwards compatibility. It received mixed reactions, with praise for its graphics, map design and deviations from the genre but criticism for its unbalanced gunplay and game mechanics. The game failed to meet expectations from players, with Ubisoft announcing that they would start overhauling the game's gameplay and systems.
On January 27, 2022, Ubisoft announced that Hyper Scape would be shutting down on April 27.

